title: SwiftTEA: Another 1989 Theory?!
description:
Taylor just won't stop and we are buying into these theories! Is 1989 really on the way? Will we be blessed with this album BEFORE Red TV? Here's why we think it could happen.
Plus, yeah we said it and it happened. What does this mean for us? And what would you like from us? Lots of ways to contact us and let us know!
